Near Clemmons / Mile Marker 182 to 182 Heading East. The Contractor for the I-0911A project (I-40 over the Yadkin River at the Davie-Forsyth County Line) is scheduled to close a ramp at Exit 182 (Harper Road) near Clemmons.The contractor will close the on-ramp from Harper Road to I-40 Eastbound on Monday (05/10) and Tuesday (5/11) from 10:00pm - 5:00am nightly. This ramp closure is necessary to safely place asphalt pavement on the ramp. Detours will be utilized for these ramp closures. A link to the detour maps is provided below.&nbsp;This work is part of the&nbsp;continuing construction to&nbsp;replace the I-40 bridges over the Yadkin River and to widen and make improvements along I-40.&nbsp;As always this work is weather dependent and may be subject to change.
